  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PowerDirector 2025 Ultimate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform ordinary footage into professional videos by harnessing powerful, advanced AI features with a user-friendly interface.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Background Remover</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flawlessly remove backgrounds from your footage or automatically cut out subjects from videos or images to add to other creations — no green screen needed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/96ebbb375fe78bf3f5fac37fb912b6b8.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/96ebbb375fe78bf3f5fac37fb912b6b8.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Speech To Text Transcription</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Render dialogue and add auto captions in many languages with automated tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/428f1caa1e445bc7821a9d8eacc5cf05.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/428f1caa1e445bc7821a9d8eacc5cf05.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Auto Face Blur</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto detect, selectively apply, and modify Mosaic and Gaussian blur effects to multiple faces in your video frames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/004f3ef285f77b7aac470d8a48cfa262.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/004f3ef285f77b7aac470d8a48cfa262.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Motion Tracking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add text, graphics, and effects that follow objects with near perfect accuracy in your clips with frame-by-frame motion tracking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/94885261df4a438f9186d42a23a9fe7a.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/94885261df4a438f9186d42a23a9fe7a.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Body Effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instantly apply striking visual effects to moving people or objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/5c468f5e9711f592ea9060042e37a38e.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/5c468f5e9711f592ea9060042e37a38e.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Audio Denoise</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-detect unwanted noises instantly and restore your audio clips in a single click with recommended tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/bdcccc55316ddcef0ea6a0205e6981a7.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/bdcccc55316ddcef0ea6a0205e6981a7.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video & Title Masks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom masks with an intuitive designer to composite and design unique titles, images, graphics, or videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/7cb26634f4f043dfc03af850f923aa09.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/7cb26634f4f043dfc03af850f923aa09.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyframe Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take total control of your projects and fine-tune effects, animations, and masks with enhanced keyframing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/38f0d0bd9b7886c150277ca55451c70b.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/38f0d0bd9b7886c150277ca55451c70b.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blending Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 9 modes to layer and blend videos and images to create surreal and impactful imagery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/d758636754191489202a8120c2e09c8f.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/d758636754191489202a8120c2e09c8f.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Screen Recording</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Record high-resolution captures in full screen or specific areas on your desktop. Plus, record computer audio, webcam, and from your microphone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/f40f1a157aa1ba0953cf41cd70ab1d18.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/f40f1a157aa1ba0953cf41cd70ab1d18.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PowerDirector 2025 Ultimate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform ordinary footage into professional videos by harnessing powerful, advanced AI features with a user-friendly interface.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Background Remover</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flawlessly remove backgrounds from your footage or automatically cut out subjects from videos or images to add to other creations — no green screen needed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/96ebbb375fe78bf3f5fac37fb912b6b8.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/96ebbb375fe78bf3f5fac37fb912b6b8.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Speech To Text Transcription</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Render dialogue and add auto captions in many languages with automated tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/428f1caa1e445bc7821a9d8eacc5cf05.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/428f1caa1e445bc7821a9d8eacc5cf05.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Auto Face Blur</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto detect, selectively apply, and modify Mosaic and Gaussian blur effects to multiple faces in your video frames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/004f3ef285f77b7aac470d8a48cfa262.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/004f3ef285f77b7aac470d8a48cfa262.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Motion Tracking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add text, graphics, and effects that follow objects with near perfect accuracy in your clips with frame-by-frame motion tracking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/94885261df4a438f9186d42a23a9fe7a.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/94885261df4a438f9186d42a23a9fe7a.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Body Effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instantly apply striking visual effects to moving people or objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/5c468f5e9711f592ea9060042e37a38e.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/5c468f5e9711f592ea9060042e37a38e.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AI Audio Denoise</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-detect unwanted noises instantly and restore your audio clips in a single click with recommended tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/bdcccc55316ddcef0ea6a0205e6981a7.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/bdcccc55316ddcef0ea6a0205e6981a7.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video & Title Masks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom masks with an intuitive designer to composite and design unique titles, images, graphics, or videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/7cb26634f4f043dfc03af850f923aa09.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/7cb26634f4f043dfc03af850f923aa09.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyframe Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take total control of your projects and fine-tune effects, animations, and masks with enhanced keyframing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/38f0d0bd9b7886c150277ca55451c70b.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/38f0d0bd9b7886c150277ca55451c70b.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blending Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 9 modes to layer and blend videos and images to create surreal and impactful imagery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/d758636754191489202a8120c2e09c8f.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras_big/d758636754191489202a8120c2e09c8f.avif?t=1754574141 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Screen Recording</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Record high-resolution captures in full screen or specific areas on your desktop. Plus, record computer audio, webcam, and from your microphone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345470/extras/f40f1a157aa1ba0953cf41cd70ab1d18.avif?t=1754574141\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.